配置文件rc.lua和rc.lua.save所在目录:
/etc/xdg/awesome
把rc.lua复制到~/.config/awesome/

/usr/share/awesome/中有icons,lib,themes

1.主题更改
beautiful.init(gears.filesystem.get_themes_dir( ) .. "yourthemes/theme.lua")
把yourthemes换成你想要的主题,有四种default,dky,xresources,zenburn

2.壁纸更改
gears.wallpaper.maximized("你壁纸的路径",s, true)
注意:壁纸路径要用""

3.布局更改
awful.layout.layouts = {
    awful.layout.suit.floating,
    awful.layout.suit.tile,
    awful.layout.suit.tile.left,
    awful.layout.suit.tile.bottom,
    awful.layout.suit.tile.top,
    awful.layout.suit.fair,
    awful.layout.suit.fair.horizontal,
    awful.layout.suit.spiral,
    awful.layout.suit.spiral.dwindle,
    awful.layout.suit.max,
    awful.layout.suit.max.fullscreen,
    awful.layout.suit.magnifier,
    awful.layout.suit.corner.nw,
    -- awful.layout.suit.corner.ne,
    -- awful.layout.suit.corner.sw,
    -- awful.layout.suit.corner.se,
}
若要去掉某个布局,只需在对应行前加上--
或者改变行的顺序.我一般只用floating, fair, spiral.dwindle三种

4.更改工作区(即虚拟桌面tags的名字)
-- Each screen has its own tag table.
awful.tag({ "1", "2", "3", "4", "5", "6", "7", "8", "9" }, s, awful.layout.layouts[1])
可以把上面那行注释掉--,然后改为:
-- Each screen has its own tag table.
local names = { "learn", "code", "movie", "music", "5", "6", "7", "8", "9" }
local l = awful.layout.suit  
local layouts = { l.floating, l.tile, l.spiral.dwindle }
awful.tag(names, s, layouts)
这样一来,local layouts里面的三种布局将以循环的形式分别对应local names里面自定义命名的tags